  "body": "### Description\r\nWhen upgrading besu-native to 0.4.x, we noticed that there were a lot of unit tests failures. All related to bls12.\r\n\r\nWe need to run a regression to identify where this was introduced. Version 0.3.0 of besu-native is the latest version that is stable for bls12.\r\n\r\nThere was a 0.3.1 release that was never used by Besu. I suspect the issues could be related to these changes (https://github.com/hyperledger/besu-native/commit/ceab94f24d9d0919831976823b4ff4e3f9d841f6).\r\n\r\nThis CircleCI job execution shows the failures: https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/hyperledger/besu/10199/workflows/ff23bf6f-bfef-421e-8d6e-ecf36ce80b0c/jobs/54381\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce (Bug)\r\n1. Update version.gradle `org.hyperledger.besu:bls12-381:0.3.0` to `org.hyperledger.besu:bls12-381:0.4.0` (or greater)\r\n2. Run `./gradlew build`\r\n",
